public class SCCVertexDataType extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple6<org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<Long,​Long>,​Boolean,​Long,​Long,​HashSet<Long>,​HashSet<Long>>
Data Type for StronglyConnectedComponents.

Tuple6, HashSet> color, sccTag, minForward, minBackward, inNbr, outNbr

For color: (i)color=(-1, -1), means not assigned; (ii)(color, color), color>=0, means founded; (iii)otherwise, (x, y), means in processing.

For sccTag: (i)sccTag = false, means not assigned; (ii)sccTag = true, means founded.

For minForward & minBackward: -1, means Uninit.
